»CL1:Wade:»CL0: You're lying. I want the truth.
      Do you or do you not believe a
PPC will give you an unfair advantage?

»CL3:Zig:»CL2: I found out that it doesn't
     matter on what cpu (hardware)
your demo was coded. It's all about
how it looks like. And if it looks
cool and people like it - you win. But
PPC could help to make much complex
effects at the same frame-rate and if
